OL,3,CCompany fined after thousands of fish
OL,4,Ckilled by sewage leaking into streams
OL,6,FA water company has been fined
OL,7,F#500,000 for sewage leaks that killed
OL,8,Fthousands of fish across Somerset and
OL,9,FWiltshire.
OL,11,FWessex Water was found to be negligent
OL,12,Fin failing to promptly report the
OL,13,Fleaks to the Environment Agency.
OL,15,FSwindon Magistrates' Court sentenced
OL,16,Fthe company to a total of #500,000
OL,17,Fafter it pleaded guilty at an earlier
OL,18,Fhearing to two charges.
