OL,3,CCompany fined after thousands of fish
OL,4,Ckilled by sewage leaking into streams
OL,6,FThe first charge related to the
OL,7,FBowerhill Lodge sewage pumping station
OL,8,Fat Melksham, in Wiltshire.
OL,10,FThe second related to a burst sewer
OL,11,Fmain at the Wick St Lawrence sewage
OL,12,Ftreatment works near Weston-super-
OL,13,FMare, in Somerset.
OL,15,FThe company was also ordered to pay
OL,16,Fcosts of #60,000, plus applicable VAT,
OL,17,Fand a victim surcharge of #170.
OL,19,FMore than 2,000 fish killed by pumping
OL,20,Fstation discharge
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/16
