OL,3,CCompany fined after thousands of fish
OL,4,Ckilled by sewage leaking into streams
OL,6,FThe two charges at Bowerhill Lodge
OL,7,Fwere for causing stormwater to
OL,8,Fdischarge into the Clackers Brook
OL,9,Fbetween March and April 2018, and
OL,10,Fdischarging screened sewage from July
OL,11,Fto August 2018.
OL,13,FThe third charge was for causing
OL,14,Funtreated sewage effluent to discharge
OL,15,Finto marsh rhynes, a type of manmade
OL,16,Fdrainage channel, from a rising main
OL,17,Fleading into the Wick St Lawrence
OL,18,Fworks.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/16
