OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F433A1731352265
OL,3,CCompany fined after thousands of fish
OL,4,Ckilled by sewage leaking into streams
OL,6,FIn a case brought by the Environment
OL,7,FAgency, the court heard more than
OL,8,F2,100 fish died in the Clackers Brook,
OL,9,Fa tributary of the River Avon, during
OL,10,Fthe discharge at Bowerhill Lodge.
OL,12,FThese included eels, lamprey and
OL,13,Fbullheads, three species which are
OL,14,Fthreatened and are also listed by the
OL,15,FInternational Union for Conservation
OL,16,Fof Nature. Investigators found almost
OL,17,Fall of the fish within a 1km reach had
OL,18,Fbeen killed.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/16
