OL,3,CCompany fined after thousands of fish
OL,4,Ckilled by sewage leaking into streams
OL,6,FThe discharge was caused by a
OL,7,Fmechanical failure and continued for
OL,8,F54.5 hours with sewage flowing through
OL,9,Fa nature conservation area. The
OL,10,Fcompany did not report this to the
OL,11,FEnvironment Agency immediately.
OL,13,FFailures in alarm system meant
OL,14,Fdischarges went unnoticed
OL,16,FThe investigation found that failures
OL,17,Fof the sewage pumping station's alarm
OL,18,Fand telemetry system, and a power
OL,19,Fcable becoming entangled in pump
OL,20,Fequipment, contributed to the failures.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/16
