OL,3,CCompany fined after thousands of fish
OL,4,Ckilled by sewage leaking into streams
OL,6,FFurther investigation found that there
OL,7,Fhad been other discharges from
OL,8,FBowerhill Lodge Pumping Station
OL,9,Fearlier that year that Wessex Water
OL,10,Fhad not reported to the Environment
OL,11,FAgency.
OL,13,FAt Wick St Lawrence, much of the local
OL,14,Frhyne was affected by sewage, leading
OL,15,Fto fish, including spined stickleback
OL,16,Fand eels, dying after a rising main (a
OL,17,Fpipe through which sewage is pumped
OL,18,Funder pressure) burst.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/16
