OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F433A1731352265
OL,3,CCompany fined after thousands of fish
OL,4,Ckilled by sewage leaking into streams
OL,6,FThe Environment Agency said that
OL,7,FWessex Water's rising mains are ageing
OL,8,Fand becoming vulnerable to bursting
OL,9,Fand the company had predicted it would
OL,10,Fneed to replace them at nine times its
OL,11,Fcurrent rate to remain stable.
OL,13,FBetween 2015 and 2023, six of the 28
OL,14,Fserious pollution incidents caused by
OL,15,FWessex Water have arisen from rising
OL,16,Fmains, accounting for 21% of serious
OL,17,Fincidents during that period, it said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/16
