OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F433A1731352265
OL,3,CCompany fined after thousands of fish
OL,4,Ckilled by sewage leaking into streams
OL,6,FDistrict Judge Joanna Dickens said
OL,7,Fthat the company's failure to report
OL,8,Fdischarges at Bowerhill Lodge
OL,9,F"undermines the regulatory regime"
OL,10,Fthough Wessex Water had since taken
OL,11,F"considerable and expensive steps" to
OL,12,Fremedy the situation.
OL,14,FShe noted that at Wick St Lawrence,
OL,15,Fflow pressure monitoring equipment had
OL,16,Fbeen installed since the incident and
OL,17,Fthere had been no repetition of any
OL,18,Fsimilar incidents.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/16
