OL,3,CCompany fined after thousands of fish
OL,4,Ckilled by sewage leaking into streams
OL,6,FThe judge said that while there was no
OL,7,Flong-lasting impact to the environment
OL,8,Fin this case "it was negligent because
OL,9,Fof the failures at this specific
OL,10,Flocation and the failure to install
OL,11,Fmonitoring equipment at an earlier
OL,12,Ftime".
OL,14,FAgeing system poses a 'risk to people
OL,15,Fand the environment'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/16
