OL,3,CCompany fined after thousands of fish
OL,4,Ckilled by sewage leaking into streams
OL,6,FFollowing the case, the Environment
OL,7,FAgency's senior environment officer,
OL,8,FJanine Maclean, said: "These cases are
OL,9,Ffurther examples of a water company
OL,10,Fbreaking the law and causing serious
OL,11,Fpollution.
OL,13,F"It was very sad the pollution had
OL,14,Fsuch serious impacts - killing fish
OL,15,Fand other aquatic life.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/16
