OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F433A1731352265
OL,3,CCompany fined after thousands of fish
OL,4,Ckilled by sewage leaking into streams
OL,6,F"Wessex Water's rising mains are
OL,7,Fageing and becoming vulnerable to
OL,8,Fbursting and are an area of increasing
OL,9,Fconcern to the Environment Agency,
OL,10,Fpresenting risk to people and the
OL,11,Fenvironment.
OL,13,F"We recognise the company is
OL,14,Fincreasing its monitoring of rising
OL,15,Fmains, which is a positive step
OL,16,Fforward, but monitoring is still
OL,17,Freliant on failure, and we would like
OL,18,Fto see the company significantly
OL,19,Fincrease the level of investment it
OL,20,Fmakes to proactively replace rising
OL,21,Fmains before they fail.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/16
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
