PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F433A1731352265
OL,3,CCompany fined after thousands of fish
OL,4,Ckilled by sewage leaking into streams
OL,6,F"We expect all water companies to
OL,7,Fmanage and maintain their sewage
OL,8,Fpumping stations and rising mains in a
OL,9,Fresponsible and sustainable manner to
OL,10,Fensure they do not cause pollution.
OL,12,F"We hope these cases send a clear
OL,13,Fsignal to shareholders and water
OL,14,Fcompany board rooms, up and down the
OL,15,Fcountry, that investing in resilient
OL,16,Fsewage systems to prevent pollution,
OL,17,Fand ensure compliance, must be an
OL,18,Fessential way of doing business.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/16
