OL,4,Ckilled by sewage leaking into streams
OL,6,F"Our dedicated officers are increasing
OL,7,Four regulatory inspections of Wessex
OL,8,FWater's sewage pumping stations and we
OL,9,Fwill also be attending more incidents,
OL,10,Fincluding those arising from rising
OL,11,Fmains, with the new resources we are
OL,12,Fgaining to transform the way we
OL,13,Fregulate the water industry."
OL,15,FResponse from Wessex Water - 'This
OL,16,Fshouldn't have happened and we're
OL,17,Fsorry'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/16
