OL,3,CCompany fined after thousands of fish
OL,4,Ckilled by sewage leaking into streams
OL,6,FA Wessex Water spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"These incidents six years ago were
OL,8,Fcaused by a burst sewerage pipe and a
OL,9,Fmechanical issue that both sadly
OL,10,Fresulted in fish dying.
OL,12,F"This shouldn't have happened and
OL,13,Fwe're sorry.
OL,15,F"Once the problems were identified, we
OL,16,Fquickly took action to minimise
OL,17,Fenvironmental harm and carried out
OL,18,Femergency repairs.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/16
