OL,3,CCompany fined after thousands of fish
OL,4,Ckilled by sewage leaking into streams
OL,6,F"Since these incidents took place, we
OL,7,Fhave invested in AI technology to
OL,8,Fdetect where potential issues on our
OL,9,Fnetwork might occur to further protect
OL,10,Fthe environment.
OL,12,F"We're planning a step change in the
OL,13,Fmaintenance of our sewerage network
OL,14,Fand, if approved by our regulators,
OL,15,Fare proposing to spend #300m in this
OL,16,Farea by 2030."
